{"word":"G3884 - παραλογίζομαι - paralogízomai - par-al-og-id'-zom-ahee - Beguile","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραλογίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paralogízomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-al-og-id'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beguile</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வஞ்சி"},{"paragraph":"1. to reckon wrong, to miscount"},{"paragraph":"2. to cheat by false reckoning"},{"paragraph":"3. to deceive, delude, circumvent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G3049 - λογίζομαι - logízomai - log-id'-zom-ahee/3049\">G3049</a>; to <i>misreckon</i>, that is, <i>delude:</i> - beguile, deceive.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}